data.description: 2 story, 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom, double garage, stainless steel appliances, ceiling fans, central hvac, tile floors, hardwood front door, smart home. Sprinkler system, blinds on every window. Granite countertop. Huge walking closet in master bedroom. Ceiling fans with light fixtures in nook, living room, family room, flex room, master bedroom, guest bedroom. Extended patio wood deck. Smart home equipped with 5 cameras. Large kitchen sink. Master bathroom tub with sliding doors.
